title: on me by section 1(2) of the Air Navigation and Transport Act 2022 (No. 40 of
heading: 2. The 15th day of February 2023 is appointed as the day on which section
text_raw:
2. The 15th day of February 2023 is appointed as the day on which section 
69 of the Air Navigation and Transport Act 2022 (No.40 of 2022) shall come 
into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

15 February, 2023. 

EAMON RYAN, 

Minister for Transport. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 24th February, 2023.

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This Order appoints 15th February 2023 as the date on which Section 69 of the 
Air Navigation and Transport Act 2022 comes into operation.
